'''Docking Bay 66''' was a [[Hangar/Legends|docking bay]] in [[Cilpar]]'s [[Mos Tommro Spaceport]]. It was used by [[Porolo Miatamia]] when he visited the [[Planet/Legends|world]] in [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]].

